WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:07.952 --> 00:00:13.182
A long time ago in a galaxy far, far away....

00:00:15.303 --> 00:00:25.533
STAR WARS

00:00:27.726 --> 00:00:31.641
Star Wars: Episode V - The Empire Strikes Back

00:00:32.023 --> 00:00:37.428
Luke Skywalker felt the force and saw a future in which his friends die. 

00:00:37.781 --> 00:00:42.847
A mercenary Boba Fett took with him Han Solo placed in the carbonite.

00:00:43.423 --> 00:00:48.215
Leia, Chewie and Lando repulsed by the imperial storm troopers, 

00:00:48.312 --> 00:00:51.108
and then become hostages of the empire.

00:00:51.369 --> 00:00:54.883
When Luke arrived at Cloud City on the planet Bespin,

00:00:55.167 --> 00:00:59.044
he encounters Darth Vader.

00:01:51.674 --> 00:01:54.498
These weapons will not help you young Skywalker,

00:01:54.613 --> 00:01:56.765
Fight me as a real Jedi.

00:02:02.446 --> 00:02:03.052
Fine

00:02:43.714 --> 00:02:45.431
Excellent, fine!

00:02:55.313 --> 00:02:57.541
Obi-Wan taught you well.

00:03:10.436 --> 00:03:11.394
You are beaten.

00:03:11.547 --> 00:03:12.924
It is useless to resist.

00:03:13.130 --> 00:03:15.874
Don't let yourself be destroyed as Obi-Wan did.

00:03:19.360 --> 00:03:22.792
There is no escape. Don't make me destroy you.

00:03:23.078 --> 00:03:24.864
Luke, you do not yet realize your importance.

00:03:25.054 --> 00:03:27.035
You have only begun to discover your power,

00:03:27.301 --> 00:03:29.799
join me and I will complete your raining. 

00:03:29.800 --> 00:03:33.584
With our combined strength, we can end this destructive conflict 

00:03:33.584 --> 00:03:35.072
and bring order to the galaxy.

00:03:35.073 --> 00:03:37.073
I'll never join you!

00:03:37.151 --> 00:03:39.728
If you only knew the power of the dark side.

00:03:39.861 --> 00:03:42.224
Obi-Wan never told you what happened to your father.

00:03:43.268 --> 00:03:46.452
He told me enough! It was you who killed him.

00:03:47.826 --> 00:03:50.472
No. I am your father.

00:03:51.044 --> 00:03:55.891
No. No. That's not true! That's impossible!

00:03:56.073 --> 00:04:00.114
Search your feelings. You know it to be true.

00:04:01.510 --> 00:04:04.526
No!  No!

00:04:05.103 --> 00:04:07.861
Luke. You can destroy the Emperor.

00:04:07.862 --> 00:04:10.418
He has foreseen this. It is your destiny.

00:04:10.474 --> 00:04:13.761
Together we can rule the galaxy as father and son.

00:04:20.479 --> 00:04:23.271
Come with me.  It is the only way.

00:04:24.247 --> 00:04:29.671
Luke, wait, I want to give you this drink, he will give you new strength!

00:04:29.672 --> 00:04:32.683
I just want to drink it with you!

00:04:32.683 --> 00:04:34.775
Let's talk as father and son.

00:04:41.029 --> 00:04:43.261
Oh yes, you were right!

00:04:44.006 --> 00:04:46.068
I'm always right, my son!

00:05:04.971 --> 00:05:07.218
Well, for the galaxy!

00:05:12.942 --> 00:05:14.098
For the galaxy!

